TITLE: Perceiving attitude change: How qualitative shifts augment change perception

COMMENT: As there were many possible p-values to choose from, the first reported dependent variable was chosen (Accountability) according to the Coding protocol (Section 3.1.2). Additionally, exact p-values were not reported for P2 and P3, so these were estimated by attempted re-analysis in R. This prompted a need to make a decision on how to deal with p-values not reported exactly. Furthermore, as no appropriate control studies had been coded previously to this study, the control study was the next consecutively coded appropriate study (i.e. with 4 studies).
